r base beyond the socialites who are prone to flashbacks of that kooky shift mummy wore to cocktails at the slocums in newport we ca n't look back all our lives to the 1960 's ms pucci who came to fashion by way of degrees in politics and economics added the most precious thing my father left to me was not his archive but his spirit we intend to make this a durable fashion brand

